{"tid":2437973,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"報道指國泰取回15條港龍中港航線經營許可 佔原本營運內地22個航點逾60%","createTime":"2021-03-08T07:59:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T07:59:57.000Z","uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"95fd08bbaa3cfe6496acb1b1ca60a12fdbd1604f","tid":2437973,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T07:59:57.000Z","msg":"報道指國泰(<a href=\"http://00293.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00293.HK&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ddb88e30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00293.HK</a>)取得15條港龍中港航線經營許可<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報道，中國民用航空局公布向國泰(<a href=\"http://00293.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00293.HK&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058mLZ6li1RkmcNQmTobTGNbY%3D&h=ddb88e30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00293.HK</a>)  -0.380 (-5.128%)    沽空 $7.27百萬; 比率 9.622%   批出15條原本由港龍營運、來往本港及內地城市的航線經營許可，涉及南京、杭州及廈門等城市，航線數目佔港龍原本營運內地22個航點逾60%，不限於客貨運及每周開辦航班的數量。"}]}